headline: FIS Launches Securities Matching Solution to Help Maximize Efficiencies for the U.S. Securities Finance Industry
summary: JACKSONVILLE, Fla., April 02, 2025--FIS® (NYSE: FIS), a global leader in financial technology, today announced the launch of its new Securities Finance Matching Platform in the U.S., following the completion of its SEC filing process. The cloud-native solution employs smart automated matching technology for secure, scalable and cost-effective securities finance for broker-dealers.
